OL,3,CGraveyards being made safer after
OL,4,Cdeath of young boy
OL,6,FSafety work has started on graveyards
OL,7,Fafter a young boy died due to a
OL,8,Ffalling gravestone.
OL,10,FEli Testa, 4, died in hospital from
OL,11,Fhis injuries after the cross on top of
OL,12,Fa gravestone at Rawtenstall Cemetery
OL,13,Fin Rossendale, Lancashire, fell on top
OL,14,Fof him on 5 July 2025.
OL,16,FRossendale Council has now confirmed
OL,17,Fthat the first phase of safety
OL,18,Fmeasures have been completed at four
OL,19,Fcemeteries in Rawtenstall, Bacup,
OL,20,FWhitworth and Haslingden, making them
OL,21,Ftemporarily safe for visitors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
